{"tid":1832423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣州市第八人民醫院下令全體員工取消春節外出休假","createTime":"2020-01-21T07:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T07:10:22.000Z","uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"efd5849a67d3561d6f4982530eb3d9bc9874d6f7","tid":1832423,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案飆升，疫情蔓延至多個南方城市。廣州市互聯網信息辦公室在官方微博表示，專門接收和診治傳染病病人的廣州市第八人民醫院，下令醫院全體員工取消春節外出休假，要留在廣州待命。<br />\n<br />\n微博又指出，廣州八院已經成立「專家指導組」，每日安排值班人員留守醫院，騰出200張床位接收相關病人，醫院園區亦有一座大樓隨時候命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1503951_1_20200121140642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1503951_1_20200121140642.jpg&h=73d557c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503951-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503951-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6jKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=ba038317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503951-20200121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=71df4e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503951-20200121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0968864ebe5be5be0ea34d4d7fa3cc04c956fbd0","tid":1832423,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"殺哂d病人就得啦"},{"pid":"291f5bc695c3e4b984cd2fbef08b254802f9563b","tid":1832423,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"支那蝗族死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"h